  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">RFC1123Date = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:string/0">string</a>() | undefined</pre>

        </div>


<p><a href="#rfc1123_date/0"><code class="inline">rfc1123_date/0</code></a> returns the current date in RFC 1123 format. <code class="inline">rfc_date/1</code>
converts the date in the Erlang format to the RFC 1123 date format.</p>
